{"type": "article", "id": 16078, "title": "Nendo的新作：用黑色的点和线，组成一个桌子", "description": "房间的拐角似乎很难处理，这些桌子帮你好好利用。话说，这真是一个很厉害的设计工作室啊！", "date": "2015-10-14T18:02:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 17210, "name": "设计展"}, {"id": 2284, "name": "桌子"}, {"id": 17211, "name": "实验设计"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 286, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031204061mx3GgnkvfPX6yZi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Nendo 在东京的 Eye of Gyre 画廊里展出了一套名为“border table”的桌子，以探讨家具和空间的关系。所有的展示都是用 5 平方毫米粗的黑色金属棒和直径 20 厘米的圆形小桌面搭建，依靠墙壁摆设，用来模拟家具的外形和放置的位置。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120356E4GOCdLxksc7IJ90.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t白色的墙让整个空间看上去近乎透明，仅靠黑色的金属棒勾勒出轮廓，像随意画上去的路线草图。圆形的小桌面与长条金属棒构成对比，垂直相切或者平行，是点和线的运动变化。桌子在任何空间里做无限变换，安放的位置看上去也很随意，代表了能适应各种空间的家具实体。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120357CyRfsVoGAX3unEF4.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"578\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120357gPDs84AJpfQZ6Txc.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120357RFukG23P1WzAMr5I.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120358z7DQBeC3lN2mfxVA.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120358Yxn2EwmZD7uiR8ft.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120358vsCRoPmOz3Wt02wg.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120359sythwBA1Wko3unXY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120359lxjmSteVGJRphkH1.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120401QJxXqosuvNk5frcd.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607031204011LmaM9XVCvrsNDdO.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120402xse482cqipoOMz1P.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261434510srJPWj3EaYlL2yd.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120402VmUQNsaRXyWfI5Pg.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120403tJC80Uxy69A1rZfz.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120403LZWSzRT7mpie25YH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120403cVLtprsRmGlxz3Nf.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607031204046cTZvlCsBYmFqoaA.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120404X9V2UBPCmIpL01hG.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"1229\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49878049\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t有趣的是，黑色的金属棒在接近墙的一端有时会渐变到白色，像是融进了白色的背景墙面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120404Ix0HfrQjXqKshela.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"1229\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49878049\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120405eOPhItEX0KyNSQrj.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t布展最困难之处是如何保持平衡，这些桌子都仅靠自身力量支撑。Nendo 团队利用了墙面的转折处，就是普遍被认为比较麻烦的角落或柱子，同时精密地计算了比例，让小型盆景能放在圆桌面上，绿色的植物也是生机的象征，让这些桌子回归到生活。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120405B5NJ6S3cfV4l7zsq.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"1093\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33292683\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tNendo 最初想要打破家具在大规模生产下的平均规格配置，探讨家具和有凸出柱子的墙面的关系。不过，这些桌子的设计拥有简洁优雅的装饰性，更像是一场艺术秀。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.cn/news/show.php?itemid=6409\" target=\"_blank\">designboom</a><a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/border-table-2/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\"> nendo</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}